&lt;ul style=&quot;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;giving oneself airs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39; is an&amp;nbsp;idiom that means&lt;em&gt; &amp;#39;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;act pretentiously or snobbishly.&lt;/em&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;giving oneself airs&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;means&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;acting in a way that shows one thinks one is better than other people&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
